# Log files directory
# JSONL log files are written here, split by source:
#
# - web.jsonl      : Web frontend requests (browser)
# - cli.jsonl      : CLI operations
# - mobile.jsonl   : Mobile application requests
# - telegram.jsonl : Telegram bot interactions
# - api.jsonl      : Direct API calls (integrations)
# - database.jsonl : Database operations and queries
# - tasks.jsonl    : Background tasks and scheduled jobs
# - internal.jsonl : Internal service operations
# - unknown.jsonl  : Requests without source identification
#
# Files are automatically rotated at 10MB with 5 backups kept.
# Add *.jsonl to .gitignore to prevent committing log data.
